Implement the markdown CRUD emitter against the runtime crate.

The `epic` field is a `belongs_to` foreign key and the `tags` list is the
authoritative side of a many-to-many — both stored as Obsidian wikilinks,
so this file is a graph node in any vault tool. Generated code strips the
brackets at its typed boundary; on disk they stay link-shaped.
